{"product_id":"norrskin-night-repair-face-mask-50ml","title":"NorrSkin Night Repair Face Mask 50ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eMoisturises, soothes and repairs your skin, supports the renewal of the epidermis. Rich in vitamins and minerals, non-comedogenic.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eBenefits: \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eRepairs damaged and tired skin while bringing back natural healthy look\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eBalance oil\/sebum production with Niacinamide\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eIt softens skin texture with Jojoba Oil and Linseed oil\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMineralise and boost your skin with vitamins\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eIt smoothes skin and prevents irritations\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eDeeply nourishes and repairs skin immune barrier with the power of Niacinamide and Linseed extract\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eIt reduces appearance of fine lines and wrinkles\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e When used daily it has strong anti-aging benefits\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eSqualane\u003c\/span\u003e protects the skin from water loss. Deeply moisturises the skin, has a mild formula, making it suitable for sensitive skin, regulates production of sebum, has a strong anti-aging effect.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eLinseed Oil\u003c\/span\u003e is extra-rich, plant-derived source of Omega-3 fatty acids. Provides a nourishing lipid barrier.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eAloe Vera Gel\u003c\/span\u003e is soothing, anti-bacterial, anti-fungal, cleansing and moisturising.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e97,5% natural origin ingredients, dermatologically tested.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Apply a generous amount of the mask on clean skin. Leave for 10-15 minutes. Massage remaining part into the skin. Use regularly 1-2 times a week.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Linum Usitatissimum Seed Oil, Squalane, Cetearyl Alcohol, Glycerin, Glyceryl Stearate Citrate, Glyceryl Stearate, Aloe Barbadensis Leaf Juice, Butyrospermum Parkii Butter, 1,2-Hexanediol, Simmondsia Chinensis Seed Oil, Hamamelis Virginiana Water, Linum Usitatissimum Seed Extract, Fragaria Vesca Fruit Extract, Sodium Hyaluronate, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil, Tocopherol, Pantolactone, Panthenol, Xanthan Gum, Parfum, Lactic Acid, Sodium Phytate, Sodium Benzoate, Potassium Sorbate, Hydroxyacetophenone, Linalool, Citronellol, Hexyl Cinnamal. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eNatural Certified | Clean Certified | Vegan Certified\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eInspired by Hälsingland, Sweden.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eNorrSkin plants 1 tree for every product sold.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"bioskina","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49308422603079,"sku":null,"price":36.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/norrskin-night-repair-face-mask-50ml-403415.png?v=1739897341","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/products\/norrskin-night-repair-face-mask-50ml","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}